00:10.511 --> 00:11.929
♪ Yonder! Yonder!
Wander! Yonder! ♪

00:12.012 --> 00:14.223
♪ Yip bi di dit bip bi-ee-i-di-dit
Wander Over Yonder! ♪

00:14.306 --> 00:16.808
♪ Yip bi di dit bip bi-ee-i-di-dit
Wander Over Yonder! ♪

00:16.892 --> 00:19.603
♪ Yip bi di dit bip bi-ee-i-di-dit
Wander Over Yonder! ♪

00:19.686 --> 00:21.021
♪ Wander! Wander!
Over! Over! ♪

00:21.104 --> 00:22.439
♪ Yonder! Yonder!
Wander! Yonder! ♪

00:22.523 --> 00:24.775
♪ Yip bi di dit bip bi-ee-i-di-dit
