00:26.151 --> 00:30.113
(LORD HATER LAUGHS)

00:32.908 --> 00:35.577
♪ Yip bi di dit bip bi-ee-i-di-dit
Wander Over Yonder! ♪

00:35.661 --> 00:37.829
♪ Yip bi di dit bip bi-ee-i-di-dit
Wander Over Yonder! ♪

00:37.913 --> 00:39.414
♪ Wander! Wander!
Over! Over! ♪

